OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine
OL,6,Fevening, although some high cloud may
OL,7,Flimit sunshine across southern coasts.
OL,8,FMost parts staying dry overnight,
OL,9,Fhowever further lower cloud is
OL,10,Fexpected spread westwards overnight,
OL,11,Fperhaps with the odd spot of drizzle.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FA cloudy start for many, but
OL,14,Fsimilar to Monday, this cloud will
OL,15,Fburn away through the morning to leave
OL,16,Fa largely sunny day. Very warm or hot
OL,17,Fagain in places.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
