OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FLargely dry through this period, with
OL,7,Fcloud developing overnight, burning
OL,8,Faway by day to give sunny spells.
OL,9,FStaying very warm or hot, especially
OL,10,Finland, but cooler along some eastern
OL,11,Fcoasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
